                    <h2 class="mb-4">Affiliation</h2>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Sree Muthukumaraswamy College,</strong> established in 1997, is the self-financing affiliated college located in Kodungaiyur, Chennai. The institution is affiliated to the University of Madras, under whose academic regulations it offers a range of Undergraduate, Postgraduate and Research programs including B.Com., B.Sc., BCA, BA, BBA, M.Com., M.Sc. and Ph.D. courses. As an affiliated college, it follows the curriculum, examination and degree-awarding framework prescribed by the University of Madras, ensuring that its academic standards align with university norms.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        The college strictly adheres to the curriculum, examination systems and quality benchmarks outlined by the affiliating university. Our faculty actively participate in university-level academic activities, workshops and committees, contributing to the continuous improvement of higher education standards.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="mt-5 mb-4">Accreditation</h2>

                    <p>
                        <strong>Sree Muthukumaraswamy College,</strong> is currently under the process of NAC accreditation, demonstrating its commitment to enhancing quality in higher education. The institution is taking systematic steps to strengthen academic practices, infrastructure, student support services and governance in line with NAC guidelines. Internal quality assurance measures are being implemented to ensure continuous improvement in teaching, learning and evaluation. Through this accreditation process, the college aims to uphold transparency, accountability and excellence in all academic and administrative activities.
                    </p>

                    <h4 class="mt-5">Commitment to Quality</h4>
                    <p>
                        We are committed to achieving excellence in higher education through continuous improvement, quality assurance practices and a strong sense of responsibility toward our students and the community. Our institutional policies reflect our dedication to holistic growth and sustainable development.
                    </p>

                    <div class="text-center mt-5">
                        <img src="~/img/accreditation/affiliation.jpeg" alt="Accreditation and Affiliation" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm">
                    </div>

                </div>
